<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l14">wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Nu haben wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> nehſt auch ver = </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l15">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſchrıben . </del> / dıe <expan>gelegenh<ex>eit</ex></expan> der ſache . nehſt auch ʒu <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> maſſ <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l16">Alſo tun wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>ʒuwıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> leʒar Jud yecʒ <expan>Jm<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l17">
<add><ab facs="#facs_365_r1l1">fünften Jare </ab></add> heẅſlıch vnd weſenlıch bey vns <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt / vnd dem Reıche vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l18">vns von des Reıchs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ʒeıt ſteẅr vnd ʒınſe <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan> hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l19">vnd <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> niht vnd <expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> auch </del> niht erfarn / daʒ er <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ʒeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l20"><expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>ſprechen</expan> geſtanden oder ʒınſper oder ſteẅrbeͣr </ab>
