<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l22">Jm auch des <expan>vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hengen ſo wır es weſten / vnd mag vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l23">eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade wol gelawben / Daʒ wır vns vmb den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l24"><expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Juden / gen <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>angenome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> noch </ab>
