<ab facs="#facs_365_r2l27">von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchıken vnd beſtellen daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> leʒar Jud </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_366" id="182r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_366_r1l1">ledıg <expan>gelaſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd ſein hab dıe Jm <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> werde . Vnd was </ab>
