<ab facs="#facs_366_r1l4">gnade 
<add><ab facs="#facs_366_r1l3">aber </ab></add> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / Des welle Jm eẅr gnade <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_366_r1l5">gelawben / vnd <expan>günſtıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>beweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / als etc / das wellen . etc </ab>
